   version stable 0.1.6
   require gtk+-v1.2 libpcap jpeg libungif
  category network
 attribute new x11
    source http://www.ex-parrot.com/~chris/driftnet/driftnet-$VERSION.tar.gz
      info home  http://www.ex-parrot.com/~chris/driftnet/
      desc 'sniffs network traffic and picks out images from TCP streams
Driftnet is inspired by EtherPEG,
it is a program which listens to network traffic
and picks out images from TCP streams it observes.
Fun to run on a host which sees lots of web traffic.'

build(){
 make &&
 mkdir  -pvm 755          $DESTDIR/usr/bin &&
 install -vm 755 driftnet $DESTDIR/usr/bin
}
